data.description: Attention investors and home buyers! An incredible opportunity awaits you to build your dream home in a highly sought-after location. This expansive 0.17 acre lot is the perfect canvas for creating your own masterpiece.  With detailed plans available upon request, you can envision the endless possibilities that this land holds. The plans showcase meticulous attention to detail, ensuring that every aspect of your future home is thoughtfully designed and executed.  This residential lot not only offers ample space for your dream estate but also provides the opportunity to build an additional dwelling unit (ADU) in the back. Imagine having a separate space for guests, extended family, or even as a potential rental income source.  The location of this property is truly central, offering convenience and accessibility to all that you desire. Take advantage of this prime location by building your home here and enjoy the tremendous upside potential of owning a million-dollar estate.  Don't miss out on this rare chance to create your own haven in an ideal setting. Drive direct and seize this remarkable opportunity today!
